---
title: Outside
sum: Fitting ideas into tiny boxes on screens.
---
<%= partial "partials/header"%>
<section id="outside">
    <article>
        <p>Welcome to the outside project. Here you can see most of the hikes I've done over the last year. We successfully completed 42 hikes in 2016 ðŸŒ¤. The goal for 2017 is to hit 104 hikes in 52 weeks. The trail maps were created in Sketch using data from <a href="//alltrails.com" target="_blank">all trails</a>. To make the UI more manageable I'm using <a href="//vuejs.org/" target="_blank">Vue.js</a>.</p>
    </article>
    <div class="notification">
        <p><strong>Note:</strong> I'm still importing hikes (digging through photos). Stay tuned for all 42!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hike-block" v-for="hike in hikes">
        <div class="meta">
            <div class="hike-header">
                <h1>{{hike.hikeName}}</h1>
                <div class="date">{{hike.hikeDate}}</div>
                <div v-bind:class="hike.hikeTrail"></div>
            </div>
            <h2><span class="icon-location"></span> {{hike.hikeLocation}}</h2>
            <h3><span class="icon-distance"></span> {{hike.hikeDistance}}</h3>
            <h3><span class="icon-elevation"></span> {{hike.hikeElevation}}</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="cover">
            <img v-bind:src="hike.hikeCover" v-bind:alt="hike.hikeName">
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- Load CDNs -->
<script src="//unpkg.com/vue@2.0.3/dist/vue.js"></script>
<script src="http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/modernizr/2.6.2/modernizr.min.js"></script>
<script src="/assets/js/outside.js"></script>
